ddddocr-go
==========

This project is a Go SDK/CLI implementation based on and referencing the
original ddddocr project:

  https://github.com/sml2h3/ddddocr

The original ddddocr project is a Python SDK for offline CAPTCHA OCR and
related CAPTCHA recognition tasks. It was developed by sml2h3 and kerlomz and
is distributed under the MIT License.

This repository includes or adapts model assets, charset data, algorithmic
behavior, and API concepts from the original project. The Go implementation,
SDK wrapper, CLI packaging, and click-captcha ordering logic in this repository
are maintained by okatu-loli.

Upstream project:

  Repository: https://github.com/sml2h3/ddddocr
